{% # Validation - Block - Richtext v1.2.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v1.2.0 — token-section is now the real production theme-root grid (drop the `display: block` override so the bleed grid + no-collapse rhythm apply, matching production). Harness chrome + the layout-neutral outline/label indicator move to the shared `validation--harness-styles` snippet (one source of truth across all validation pages). Per `validation.md` § Harness layout.
  - v1.1.0 — render richtext blocks as direct children of `<token-section>` (drop the `.block-validation-suite` flex wrapper) + base `--block-rhythm: lg`, so per-block top-margin overrides paint and the page is production-faithful. Purge the dead `narrow` / `prose:narrow` references (the `narrow` setting was removed in block v1.2.0 — width is now a `content_width` pick). Cover `content_width` / `text_color` inline via seeded handles (the spec→test recipe seeds metaobject handles, not store GIDs). Label selectors target `token-section >`. Per `validation.md` § Harness layout.
  - v1.0.0 — initial

  Block-validation harness for `richtext`. The JSON template at
  `templates/index.validation--primitive--richtext.json` bakes the test
  matrix; the section just renders them in a labelled list via
  `validation--block-labels`.

  Diagnostic intent:
  1. The snippet always emits a `prose` modifier so the global rich-
     content rules from `@layer utilities` apply (paragraph rhythm,
     list markers, link decoration).
  2. Content variants (paragraphs, lists, emphasis, links, headings)
     render with the right typography.
  3. text_align, content_width (cap + self-center), text_color, and
     top-spacing overrides apply.

  Reachable only at /?view=validation--primitive--richtext.
  See `.context/docs/validation.md`.
{% endcomment %}

{% liquid
  assign max_inline_size = section.settings.max_inline_size
  assign base_selector = 'shopify-section-' | append: section.id
%}

<token-section data-modifiers="theme-root">
  {% render 'validation--breadcrumb' %}

  <header class="validation__intro">
    <h1>Block: richtext</h1>
    <p>
      Matrix in
      <code>templates/index.validation--primitive--richtext.json</code>. Each entry is one block instance, labelled by
      its block id. The snippet always emits the <code>prose</code> modifier; variants exercise content shapes
      (paragraphs, lists, emphasis, links, headings), text alignment, the <code>content_width</code> cap, text color,
      and top-spacing overrides.
    </p>
  </header>

  {% if section.blocks.size > 0 %}
    {% content_for 'blocks' %}

    {% render 'validation--block-labels', section: section %}
  {% else %}
    <p class="validation__empty">No blocks declared in the template.</p>
  {% endif %}
</token-section>

{% capture dynamic_style %}
  {% if max_inline_size and max_inline_size != blank %}
    --max-inline-size: {{ max_inline_size }}px;
  {% endif %}
{% endcapture %}
{% render 'utility--dynamic-style', base_selector: base_selector, css_content: dynamic_style %}
{% render 'validation--harness-styles' %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Block: richtext",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section--validation--primitive--richtext",
  "blocks": [{ "type": "@theme" }],
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "max_inline_size",
      "label": "Max width",
      "min": 800,
      "max": 1920,
      "step": 20,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 1280
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
